                    "text": {
                      "value": "<b>Many people worldwide do not have access to ophthalmologists and have never taken an eye test, but a new approach enables simple mass screenings.\n</b><br/><br/>\nBy Alois Pumhösel"
                    },
                    "videoPoster": {
                      "value": "/data/media/img/der-standard/andrew-bastarous/rolex_org_partnerships_der_standard_andrew_bastawrous_posterframe.jpg"
